      <specialTip openLevel="1" key="1">Employees who use O-09-248 will take and eat a random piece of candy.</specialTip>
      <specialTip openLevel="2" key="2">Each type of candy gives different benefits for the rest of the day.</specialTip>
      <specialTip openLevel="3" key="3">There's only a limited amount of candy in the bowl. But it gets refilled every day.</specialTip>
      <specialTip openLevel="4" key="4">If an employee takes more than 1 candy, they die and get turned into more candy, and the bowl gets refilled by a small amount.</specialTip>
      <specialTip openLevel="5" key="5">When the bowl was empty and an employee who had already taken a candy tried to use O-09-248, a secret compartment opened up with 1 additional candy inside.</specialTip>
    </specialTipSize>
  </observe>
